{"tid":452021,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"所謂的「雞寶」到底是什麼？","createTime":"2017-10-29T19:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T22:40:03.000Z","uid":80551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d9ecf637027f4e7852ed3ba2e530d9ff80c83d4a","tid":452021,"uid":80551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T19:03:17.000Z","msg":"<strong>所謂的「雞寶」到底是什麼，有藥用性嗎？</strong><br />\n雞寶，是指家禽雞的膽囊結石。雞黃，別名雞寶。 在母雞產卵期間，卵巢部分發炎，輸卵管堵塞，由多個卵黃聚集在一起形成的，在民間俗稱雞靈寶，據說能治百病。雞寶完整這多成卵形，質輕，表面金黃至黃褐色。中醫學認為雞黃色清香，味微苦而後甜，性涼。可用於陽痿，早泄。月經不調等等症狀。由於天然的雞黃很珍貴，國際上的價格要高玉黃金。由於自然雞寶很珍貴，而雞的壽命至少在三年以上才有百萬分之一的「中獎率」 因此價格比黃金貴。說起動物腸胃裡的」寶「，大家比較熟知的一般都是牛黃，狗寶和馬寶，這三樣也被譽為「中藥三寶」。<br />\n很多老人都知道有雞寶，但是醫術上有沒有記載雞寶？ 它的藥用性到底是什麼，這就不得而知了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/30/030246_f58425072ef52ee4fdab6ce979a8798c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F30%2F030246_f58425072ef52ee4fdab6ce979a8798c.jpg&h=4614c31a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80fed17121d6e666bc267905dd9323ea24863612","tid":452021,"uid":5077,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T19:15:13.000Z","msg":"Sor睇錯雞竇..."},{"pid":"5a72b2c113121f890a6a914ee59ccd46b28c6c9e","tid":452021,"uid":71303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T19:25:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sor睇錯雞竇...</blockquote><br />\n+1"},{"pid":"13a57e724570b69b1f9ae64a4d39b98e6e1dc2b3","tid":452021,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T20:46:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Sor睇錯雞竇...</blockquote><br />\n咯咯"},{"pid":"3ebe3f48c4b6863cf288eaa86f1e43de2139dd44","tid":452021,"uid":120783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T21:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20140918/large/1411049412_0fa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20140918%2Flarge%2F1411049412_0fa5.jpg&h=70b4637f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"57bff01b7eb5990e5eca179896cf18fef5f52580","tid":452021,"uid":953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T22:40:03.000Z","msg":"以為 cable<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}